Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's stage is Teitan High.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And like any other school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange things happen within it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one who sees the truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dream, just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your school is haunted?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Recently our school has been bothered by ghosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pretty creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, those hauntings are always in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:02:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A student died one morning in an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And our school is cursed by his spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:10.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Two years ago. That was before I entered high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you please come investigate after school tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to see if it's real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it, leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's either some pranks or some natural occurrences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the hauntings are only in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the students don't have class then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the famous detective Mouri Kogoro's daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can I ignore these events and not reveal the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hall monitor next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're afraid to monitor alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of ghosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hit them with your karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Karate doesn't affect ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I might even find some clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:11.22,Title,,0,0,0,,Teitan High School's Ghost Story\N(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This four-eyed brat's the one who's gonna help us investigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... my dad wouldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says that such a small case doesn't need him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if this brat can help us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, the deduction queen, barely accepts him as my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What an honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are our shoe lockers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're slightly larger than your school's, right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I did go to school here for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, I'm putting your shoes in my locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran, who is this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} you always talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Isn't he cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:09.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The talkative Tashiro and Hidaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just like a mini Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even has the same expressions as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, don't become a mystery nerd when you grow up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So what if I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did you bring him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This brat with the glasses is helping us investigate,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sometimes comes in handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Investigate the ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:32.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Soccer players Aizawa and Nakamichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've come to haunt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop scaring us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you guys pass that one test?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Barely!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a close one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys need to be more careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye! Don't overwork yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you solve the hauntings, let us know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:07.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Originally I was supposed to go to school here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Learn here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Talk with my friends here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And live a normal high school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gin and Vodka...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:20.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If only I hadn't been poisoned by them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And my body didn't turn small...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}To change back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}To change back into Kudo Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:32.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I almost had the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:35.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That woman, disguised as Dr. Araide,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:37.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That woman named Vermouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She was most likely sent to kill Haibara,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:43.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The traitor of the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Although she said she had given up on Haibara,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can she be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That woman is a devil of many faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Her disguises are as good as Kaito Kid's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:59.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe she's disguised nearby right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Planning some kind of scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}W-What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dr. Araide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'd heard that after the trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd be sent to Aou Hospital to work there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was the original plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still worried about my patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And leaving you guys would also be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you'll be our school doctor again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came today to tell the school that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's really him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told by FBI agent Jodie,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That a criminal impersonated me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And planned to commit a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I temporarily went to America to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hikari-san and my grandmother weren't comfortable there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus the criminal escaped after being found out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we came back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why are you telling me these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie wanted me to tell you, and you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can help us investigate the hauntings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hauntings?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll start here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Gym Storage Room of Sorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One rainy morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gym student came here to do morning exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She heard voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming from this room which was supposed to be empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody was crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Frightened, she ran away from the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when she returned with her friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weeping had stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that was left was this desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the desk of the student who died two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosaka Hideaki's desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who would be afraid of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosaka-kun tripped on the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:40.15,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tsukamoto Kazumi\NKarate Team
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and just happened to take a bad fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't spread weird rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazumi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't there karate practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the junior that used to be the karate team captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came to investigate the hauntings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean that weeping sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:10:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everybody is saying that it was just the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wind blew through that broken window,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And people mistook it for weeping sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That this was that boy's desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told everybody the details when the rumors got out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We used to be classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is his table in here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's raining...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I didn't bring an umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's take cover until the rain stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the Library of Anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just about to head there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:58.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A signature?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, the rain's pretty heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will it stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The forecast said that it wouldn't rain for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Joining a student investigation like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really are a good-hearted guy, Dr. Araide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seko-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you? I've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, my stomach wasn't feeling well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:34.14,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kunishige Seko\NPing Pong Team
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I skipped class and took a nap in the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, why did you want to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing big. I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just rest some more and then go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before that kind-hearted doctor takes me to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was he classmates with Hosaka too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he was in a different class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he and Hosaka were childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think a jock like you spent much time in the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still read!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,College exams are next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, the library is part of our ghost tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:27.60,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Library
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So books were left out here in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's more, they were all books that Hosaka-kun had borrowed in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it happened 4 days in a row. FOUR DAYS!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could it be but Hosaka's anger at no longer being able to read his favorite books in death!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the books were left out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't the librarian notice them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because the books were all found behind shelves or under tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone's probably just fooling around,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using the ghost rumors as a scapegoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for this someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to catch him and teach him a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're going to help me, Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last place, the Cursed Stairwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One morning a student noticed that the floor here was soaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are the stairs that he died on,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the liquid was the cursed tears of Hosaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:34.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it because it rained and the windows weren't closed well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We aren't like you. Of course we closed the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's not all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a different number of steps each time you count!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you two count it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:13:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, how many?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I counted twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I counted thirteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The correct number was twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} got to the last step,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She counted it twice, once for each foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was too frightened, so she messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, then I'll count it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:32.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Do you want to solve the mystery or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you be more quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't concentrate on painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:38.54,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Monobe Masao\NArt Club
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? That student...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? The rain stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's head home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s explanations,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have more courage to stay alone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, its getting dark out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That table...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's something on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My hatred has not dissolved yet..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The paper isn't wet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So these things were moved here after the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ground is wet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So something should be present, but isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The footprints of the person who moved these things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The table and chair in the courtyard
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are the ones we just saw in the storage room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, they ore the table and chair of Hosaka Hideaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who died two years ago in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who moved them to the courtyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there was a note on the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it wasn't wet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So someone moved it there otter the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The courtyard's dirt was all wet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we arrived at the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were only footprints of Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosaka's ghost must have moved it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible, since ghosts don't leave footprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The table and chair disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? How can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} and I moved them back to the storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It other students see it, there might be a riot,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of the strange words on the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Strange words?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were roughly written words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My hatred has not dissolved yet...'1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So the paper wasn't wet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the ghost was covering it, writing words of hate on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on, stop it already...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-He is still angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost hauntings are Hosaka's curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew this student called Hosaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He and I were both art students.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two years ago, he fell down the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You were present then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:17.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This student was there that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you guys leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I con prepare for the competition,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My teacher put me in this art room to paint alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't waste any more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go tell Kazumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r} about the table in the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:53.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:00.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wax?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, when the bottom of the stairs were wet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did the floor boards get wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the whole floor was wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All because of the tears of Hosaka, who died here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was an art student who came early...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosaka's table and chair were moved to the courtyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, and on the table was a note saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My hatred has not dissolved yet..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, when will the pranks stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we catch the culprit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We two are going to grab his neck, pull him in, and teach him a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he'll die with just one hit of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, the books that Hosaka read before,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:20:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know which ones they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All these books are so complex...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, look at these borrow logs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These four books were practically only borrowed by Hosaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because Hosaka wanted to be a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To draw interesting things,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He studied what others rarely looked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:25.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told me himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know the signature on his table?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that it was for if he became famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So everyone knows that it is his signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe his anger is from not fulfilling his dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With cursing tears, he soaked the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And at midnight he perused the books he once read.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, he moved his lonely belongings to the courtyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:20:59.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Enough with the drama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the courtyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we ask the principal, we might get some clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you guys left the library,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On my way to the restroom, from the third floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sow the principal standing in the courtyard, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? He's fretting over the trees he planted in the courtyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He goes there every day and complains about those trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:32.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's still worrying about those trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? But didn't you know that, since he told you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:43.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course he didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:49.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Because the Araide{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-sensei{\r\be10}, at that time, was actually Vermouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:51.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:53.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Since Vermouth was Araide{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-sensei{\r\be10},
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:55.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She should've been the elementary school's doctor as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.51,0:21:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm eighteen, very close to your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:03.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Haibara, traitor of the organization, is about twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.79,0:22:06.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If Vermouth wanted to look for her in schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:09.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She'd look in high schools and colleges.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:11.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But if she knew that Haibara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:14.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Took the same poison I did and turned small,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:18.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why didn't she notice while at Teitan Elementary?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:23.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A transfer student should catch her attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:24.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So why didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:27.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:28.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.09,0:22:30.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Because of this haunting case,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:32.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I have another mystery to solve!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.14,0:24:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still in this school!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you gather everyone by the door of the art room?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.97,0:24:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought of a way to catch the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.47,0:24:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why don't we all just stay still and wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.81,0:24:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.84,0:24:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.21,0:24:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the spirit of Hosaka to float down the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.41,0:24:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.74,0:24:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.77,0:24:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For making this show possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.54,0:24:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.37,0:24:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.14,0:24:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weeping Storage Room,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.81,0:24:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Library of Anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.47,0:24:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Cursed Stairwell...
